      <title>费城联储指数飙升，初请失业金人数稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-18/jobless-claims-steady-as-philadelphia-fed-index-surges-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据劳工部数据，截至 4 月 13 日当周，美国首次申请失业救济人数为 212,000 人。彭博社经济学家调查的预测中位数为 215,000。费城联储调查意外升至 15.5，为两年来的最高值。迈克·麦基报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-18/jobless-claims-steady-as-philadelphia-fed-index-surges-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 13:01:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
